# Datasets & Data Sources

## Supported Datasets

### 1. Battery Archive (NREL)
**URL:** https://batteryarchive.org/  
**Contents:** Cycle aging data for 18650 cells (LFP, NMC), constant-current and pulse tests  
**Use in this project:** SOH validation, capacity fade calibration

**Download steps:**
1. Register at https://batteryarchive.org/
2. Select cell chemistry (NMC recommended for this project)
3. Download CSV cycle data files
4. Place in `data/raw/battery_archive/`

### 2. Volta Foundation Data Repository
**URL:** https://data.voltafoundation.org/  
**Contents:** Multi-format battery characterization data  
**Use in this project:** OCV–SOC curve fitting, EIS data for parameter estimation

### 3. CALCE Battery Research Group
**URL:** https://calce.umd.edu/battery-data  
**Contents:** Capacity fade for INR18650-MH1 cells at various temperatures and C-rates

### 4. Stanford Battery Dataset (SNL)
**URL:** https://data.matr.io/1/  
**Contents:** 124 LFP/graphite cells, various fast-charging protocols  
**Use in this project:** Fast-charging protocol comparison, cycle life prediction

### 5. Oxford Battery Degradation Dataset
**URL:** https://ora.ox.ac.uk/objects/uuid:03ba4b01-cfed-46d3-9b1a-7d4a7bdf6fac  
**Contents:** 8 LCO 18650 cells, 50mHz–20kHz EIS at various SOCs

