## Validation

After fitting, validate SPM predictions against dataset:

```matlab
% Run SPM with fitted parameters
out = runSPM(spm, profile_from_data, battParams, false, []);

% Compare voltage
figure;
plot(data.time/60, data.voltage, 'k-', 'LineWidth', 2, 'DisplayName', 'Experiment');
hold on;
plot(out.time/60, out.voltage, 'r--', 'LineWidth', 1.5, 'DisplayName', 'SPM');
xlabel('Time (min)'); ylabel('Voltage (V)');
legend; title('Voltage Validation');

% RMSE
rmse_V = sqrt(mean((interp1(data.time, data.voltage, out.time) - out.voltage).^2));
fprintf('Voltage RMSE: %.4f V\n', rmse_V);
```
